// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-1825 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 100ace43-f417-595a-bf2e-873534efff7d

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:12.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:12.10*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:13.04*")
